title:
Constantly curved holomorphic two-spheres in the complex Grassmannian
  G(2,6) with constant square norm of the second fundamental form
authors: Jie Fei, Ling He, Jun Wang
abstract:
We completely classify all noncongruent linearly full totally unramified
constantly curved holomorphic two-spheres in G(2,6) with constant square norm
of the second fundamental form. They turn out to be homogeneous.
